radio_info.short: KOFG is a ministry of Tres Hermanas Educational Media Foundation of Texas, Inc. The station is under the direction of Lonnie "Doc" Horton with a
radio_info.rest:
very capable assistant, my dear wife, Edna.

Our purpose is to reach as many souls for our Lord Jesus Christ as possible within the outreach of our radio signal. This station operates without making any pleas for funds over the air. Our pleas are for lost souls and the encouragement of our Christian brothers and sisters in Christ to "take a stand" for our Lord in these days of apostasy of falling away from the faith.

Our prayer is that through the programming of the "Old Fashion Gospel", our listeners that are searching for that "something" that will give them peace of mind and happiness into their lives, will find it by placing their "faith and trust" in the Lord Jesus Christ. He is the answer!

"The Lord is not slack concerning His promise, as some men count slackness, but is longsuffering to us-ward, not willing that any should perish, but that all should come to repentance." 2nd Peter 3:9 (KJV)

We take this stand for our Lord and reference Psalm 34 as my testimony of the saving Grace of my Lord Jesus Christ.

"Doc" Horton
